    code: 'public class GraphDFS {\n  private Map<Integer, List<Integer>> adj = new HashMap<>();\n  public boolean hasCycle() {\n    Set<Integer> visited = new HashSet<>();\n    for (Integer node : adj.keySet()) {\n      if (dfs(node, visited)) return true;\n    }\n    return false;\n  }\n  private boolean dfs(Integer node, Set<Integer> visited) {\n    if (visited.contains(node)) return true;\n    visited.add(node);\n    for (Integer neighbor : adj.getOrDefault(node, List.of())) {\n      if (dfs(neighbor, visited)) return true;\n    }\n    return false;\n  }\n}',
